high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the counter.
Take the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the shelves.
Place the knife on the black plate on the second shelf.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it.
Turn right and walk to the counter, then turn left and take two steps, then turn right and take one step, then turn left and walk across the room.
Place the plate and the knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left at the wall to face the counter.

Put the knife on top of the black plate on the middle shelf.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it from the shelf.
Turn right, hang a left just before the black stools and walk to the sink on your left across the room.
Put the plate with the knife in the sink.
